com.pacman.game
Class Level

java.lang.Object
  com.pacman.game.Level

public class Level
extends java.lang.Object

This class holds all the information specific to a certain level, such as the maze layout and the speeds of the objects. This enables to easily define different levels. This class also increases the score when pacman eats different objects.

Author:
Thaer
